B.adO=new A.J4("Welcome to UniFind, the student marketplace and lost & found platform for Montclair State University. By creating an account and using UniFind, you agree to the following terms. Please read them carefully. If you do not agree, you may not use the platform.",null)
B.bA=new A.bL(null,20,null,null)
B.aeb=new A.ee("1","Eligibility","UniFind is exclusively available to current Montclair State University students and faculty. You must be at least 18 years of age and register with a valid @montclair.edu email address. By registering, you confirm that all information you provide is accurate and up to date.",null,null)
B.ae3=new A.ee("2","Account Responsibility","You are solely responsible for all activity that occurs under your account. You must keep your login credentials confidential and must not share your account with anyone else. UniFind is not liable for any loss or damage resulting from unauthorized access to your account.\n\nIf you believe your account has been compromised, please contact us immediately.",null,null)
B.ae5=new A.ee("3","Acceptable Use","UniFind is a community platform built on mutual respect. All users are expected to behave professionally and courteously at all times. The following are strictly prohibited:\n\n\u2022 Posting content that is racist, sexist, homophobic, transphobic, or otherwise discriminatory\n\u2022 Harassment, threats, or intimidation of any other user\n\u2022 Impersonating another person or entity\n\u2022 Using the platform for any illegal activity\n\u2022 Attempting to manipulate, spam, or defraud other users\n\u2022 Posting false, misleading, or deliberately inaccurate information","\u26a0 Violations of these rules may result in immediate and permanent suspension from the platform.",null)
B.aea=new A.ee("4","Prohibited Items","UniFind is intended for the exchange of everyday goods within the MSU community. The following items are strictly prohibited:\n\n\u2022 Weapons, firearms, or ammunition of any kind\n\u2022 Illegal drugs, controlled substances, or drug paraphernalia\n\u2022 Alcohol or tobacco products\n\u2022 Counterfeit, stolen, or fraudulently obtained goods\n\u2022 Prescription medications\n\u2022 Explicit, adult, or sexually suggestive content\n\u2022 Live animals\n\u2022 Any item whose sale is prohibited by local, state, or federal law\n\nUniFind reserves the right to determine, at its sole discretion, whether a listing violates this policy.",null,null)
B.ae1=new A.ee("5","Listing Standards","All marketplace listings must meet the following standards to remain active:\n\n\u2022 Insufficient description \u2014 listings must clearly describe the item\n\u2022 Unreasonable pricing \u2014 no exploitative or misleading prices\n\u2022 Personal information \u2014 no phone numbers, addresses, or sensitive data\n\u2022 Duplicate listings \u2014 the same item may not be listed multiple times\n\u2022 Prohibited content \u2014 any listing that violates Section 4\n\u2022 Misleading imagery \u2014 images must accurately represent the item\n\nUsers whose listings are repeatedly removed may have their accounts suspended or permanently banned.",null,null)
B.aec=new A.ee("6","Lost & Found","The Lost & Found feature is provided as a community service. UniFind does not guarantee the recovery of any lost item and is not responsible for any transactions or interactions that arise from a Lost & Found post. Users are encouraged to exercise caution and use good judgment when arranging item returns.",null,null)
B.ae9=new A.ee("7","Account Suspension & Banning","UniFind administrators reserve the right to suspend or permanently ban any user account at any time, with or without prior notice, for any violation of these Terms & Conditions.\n\n\u2022 Posting prohibited items or content\n\u2022 Engaging in discriminatory, hateful, or harassing behavior\n\u2022 Repeated listing violations\n\u2022 Any conduct deemed harmful to the UniFind community\n\nBanned users may not create new accounts to circumvent a suspension.",null,null)
B.ae8=new A.ee("8","Privacy","UniFind collects only the information necessary to operate the platform, including your name, MSU email address, username, age, and role. We do not sell your personal information to third parties. Your data is stored securely and used solely for the purpose of providing the UniFind service.",null,null)
B.aed=new A.ee("9","Disclaimer of Warranties",'UniFind is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We do not guarantee that the platform will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of harmful components. UniFind is not responsible for any damages arising from your use of the platform.',null,null)
B.ae6=new A.ee("10","Changes to These Terms","UniFind reserves the right to update these Terms & Conditions at any time. Continued use of the platform after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the revised terms.",null,null)
B.aee=new A.ee("11","Contact","If you have any questions about these Terms & Conditions or wish to report a violation, please reach out to the UniFind team through your MSU email.",null,null)
